    "date": "2024-07-09T23:33:51Z",
    "text": "Personal Needs Allowance Modernization Act or the PNA Modernization Act\u00a0\n\nThis bill increases the minimum monthly personal needs allowance under Medicaid for an institutionalized individual and couple from $30 to $60 and from $60 to $120, respectively. (The personal needs allowance is deducted from an individual's total income when determining the individual's contribution to the cost of institutionalized care under Medicaid.)"
